ission and Loudoun County permit themselves — I didn’t lift a finger on the paperwork. Deck was done in 10 days. The Trex Calm Shell color we chose looks incredible against our siding.","\""]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"Testimonials-module__ItA9Ha__clientProfile","children":[["$","div",null,{"className":"Testimonials-module__ItA9Ha__avatarWrapper","children":["$","$L3",null,{"src":"/showcase/img21.jpg","alt":"Deck Replacement + Railings — South Riding, VA","fill":true,"className":"Testimonials-module__ItA9Ha__avatar","sizes":"65px"}]}],["$","div",null,{"className":"Testimonials-module__ItA9Ha__clientInfo","children":[["$","h4",null,{"children":"David K."}],["$","span",null,{"children":["South Riding, VA"," · ","Deck Replacement + Railings"]}]]}]]}]]}]
